<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> وُجُوبِ الزَّكَاةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلِ اللَّهِ تَعَالَى:</span> ﴿وَأَقِيمُوا الصَّلاةَ وَآتُوا الزَّكَاةَ﴾ /البقرة: ٤٣/.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span> حَدَّثَنِي أَبُو سُفْيَانَ <span class="special">﵁</span>: فَذَكَرَ حَدِيثَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَقَالَ: يَأْمُرُنَا بِالصَّلَاةِ وَالزَّكَاةِ وَالصِّلَةِ وَالْعَفَافِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ر: ٧]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>